title: Ranked status
body: I am super confused right now I had 100 point I was in silver 5 in promos now randomly I am in Placements And I know the season has not ended what is going on?

replies.body: While maintenance is going on, your profile may show as placement and it's just a visual bug.  It will return to normal once it's finished, and updates will be provided via the [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page.  Ranked games are still fine to play in the meantime as well.  Good luck!
it said they are doing some maintenance to the league system... but what I really need to know if they are still counting the points.. cause the ranked games are still available to play...
I was in a match when the maintenance started, will it be LP loss or will it update?
same thing is happening to me
